\c 5  
\p
\v 18 Don't get drunk with wine, it will make you silly, you will do bad things without thinking. Better, give yourselves to the Holy Spirit, so that he can steer you in a proper way.   
\p
\v 28 Men truly look after their bodies. Truly in that way they should look after their wives. Whoever looks after his wife is looking after himself.   